{"tid":2075641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民ifc集會悼陳彥霖","createTime":"2020-06-23T03:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T04:03:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d913ad8d59a4d4822ea08bd1dec9463af7e8762","tid":2075641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/Z46AFOEUTRZBWQHIPH3VHLU5VI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FZ46AFOEUTRZBWQHIPH3VHLU5VI%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=64afe3be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FZ46AFOEUTRZBWQHIPH3VHLU5VI%2F&h=405e24e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/Z46AFOEUTRZBWQHIPH3VHLU5VI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民ifc集會悼陳彥霖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PD75YFID4EH7V24LRMGFJ4N2CU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPD75YFID4EH7V24LRMGFJ4N2CU.jpg&h=ddf3dd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民在ifc中庭默哀致意。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾參與反修例集會的15歲女生陳彥霖去年9月被發現浮屍海面，事發至今九個月，死因依舊撲朔迷離，死因裁判庭明天就案件作研訊前檢討。有市民昨午在中環國際金融中心商場（ifc）中庭發起悼念活動，高叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死因庭明作研訊前檢討<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時左右，約10人到達ifc商場中庭，有人手持白花及陳的畫像，亦有不少人帶同標語到場，包括「光復香港時代革命」、「林奠無能」、「撐手足撐到底」等，各人先默哀再高叫口號。另有市民在樓上圍欄展示「香港獨立」標語。富商劉公子亦加入，拿着標語圍繞商場遊行叫口號。活動至下午2時許結束，在場人士和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n職訓局青年學院學生陳彥霖本身是游泳健將，多次參與反修例示威。警方去年9月22日指水警輪在油塘魔鬼山對開海面撈起一具身份不明全裸女浮屍，其後網傳關於她的尋人啟事，最後在《蘋果》多番查詢下警方才確認浮屍身份是陳彥霖。<br />\n<br />\n陳彥霖死因引來揣測，其母親及。。。。。，敲定證人名單、審訊日子等，料需時半日閉門處理，公眾及傳媒不得旁聽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6E7OIXFIKQ6NT6KWSBM4ALXFAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6E7OIXFIKQ6NT6KWSBM4ALXFAA.jpg&h=7378a3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民向陳彥霖畫像獻上鮮花。"},{"pid":"4e5607d9bea08f2cdcaa17eae884e21f968f9144","tid":2075641,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係聚焦佢同周梓樂啦, 仲有上千計犧牲者"},{"pid":"9d68074c5fb378fb4eba294342d08ed0b54b5aa4","tid":2075641,"uid":288765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e5607d9bea08f2cdcaa17eae884e21f968f9144","tid":2075641,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係聚焦佢同周梓樂啦, 仲有上千計犧牲者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"可惜苦無好實在嘅證據。。"},{"pid":"c00c6962284a3df59501319d7f8678c75a0cc65f","tid":2075641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"彥霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b747b5e3fb618cd0e54ddcea363d3ded6262c59","tid":2075641,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248e96007b80ba1d0180d9296b66078047494132","tid":2075641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00c6962284a3df59501319d7f8678c75a0cc65f","tid":2075641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"彥霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}